    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to care about anything lately. like, i was looking at the stars tonight and just thinking about how massive everything is. in a billion years, or even a trillion, none of this—none of my problems, none of my life, none of this entire species—is even going to be a memory. it feels like we're just screaming into a void that doesn't even hear us. what's the point of even trying to keep going when the end result is just total nothingness anyway?",
